        "subject": "LU-20 kernel: make bh_lru_size a kernel parameter",
        "message": "LU-20 kernel: make bh_lru_size a kernel parameter\n\nThe benefits from bh_lru_size_config.patch can only be seen\nwith Lustre. So to ease adoption of buffer head per-CPU LRU\nsize tuning in the upstream kernel, make this tuning be a\nkernel parameter instead of a kernel config option.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sebastien.buisson@bull.net>\nChange-Id: Ifad01070fdbdb585ceba1db5247b314e8777c3d8\n"
      },
